{"tid":515654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估國家)跨年不平靜　街頭砍人釀1死1傷","createTime":"2017-12-31T15:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T02:41:43.000Z","uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b44232ee698297f31c2f6188c5841a0abaa0552","tid":515654,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"日本京都市伏見區今天下午3時左右發生凶殺案，年約50歲的歹徒持刀砍傷27歲和45歲男子後逃逸，其中27歲男子胸部中刀當場宣告不治，45歲男子僅手腕受傷，沒有生命危險。<br />\n警方表示，兇手似乎認識兩名被害人，事發前一行5人在路上吵架，可能是同事間起爭執。現場目擊者表示嫌犯身穿黑衣，手持菜刀，目擊兇案的女性高喊「快一點！」，嚇壞附近向來平靜的商店街。警方還在追捕嫌犯。（陳怡妏／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"12f8940a5fc0e16c2114a4c2919e51d7391eb72f","tid":515654,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"竟然估到係日本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379674422cdceec4c63fd5c183176b6f68df5ff6","tid":515654,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"竟然估到係日本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491ae49b1a13673453d4d34521aeb2098fe29b30","tid":515654,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"竟然估到係日本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a30ead2dc04ec245211e9751a7ccf82a1365de0","tid":515654,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T02:01:09.000Z","msg":"竟然估到係日本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\